title: War Of The Roses: She Still Has The Photo Saved
description: Demetri used his girlfriends, Kim's, phone to take a picture of his dog, while he went back to look at the photo, he noticed a couple photos of a naked guy he's never seen before. We confronted both her & the suspected naked guy on the phone and couldn't tell if they were lying or not.
